":0,"text":"流量充值说明","class":"android.webkit.WebView","package":"com.ss.android.ugc.aweme","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":true,"scrollable":true,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":true,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 394, 792)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 225 - 1083, 2401)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"流量充值说明","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.ss.android.ugc.aweme","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":true,"boundsInParent":"(26, 26 - 367, 58)","boundsInScreen":"(71, 296 - 1009, 384)"},{"index":1,"text":"1、流量包到账后生效，当月有效；​","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.ss.android.ugc.aweme","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":true,"boundsInParent":"(26, 66 - 367, 92)","boundsInScreen":"(71, 406 - 1009, 478)"},{"index":2,"text":"2、流量包无提速功能，限速用户无法使用。除提速包外，流量包无法提速，限速用户下单后无法解除限速。​","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.ss.android.ugc.aweme","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":true,"boundsInParent":"(26, 101 - 367, 177)","boundsInScreen":"(71, 502 - 1009, 711)"},{"index":3,"text":"3、此流量包不支持港澳台地区以及国际漫游；不可抵扣已产生的流量，不可与副卡共享，不可转赠至其他用户。​","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.ss.android.ugc.aweme","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":true,"boundsInParent":"(26, 185 - 367, 262)","boundsInScreen":"(71, 733 - 1009, 945)"},{"index":4,"text":"4、短期流量包如日包、3天包、7天包，超时自动失效。​","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.ss.android.ugc.aweme","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":true,"boundsInParent":"(26, 270 - 367, 322)","boundsInScreen":"(71, 967 - 1009, 1110)"},{"index":5,"text":"《充值须知》\n使用充值服务前，你应当认真阅读并充分理解本充值须知。如你不同意本须知内容，将导致第三方商家无法为你提供充值服务。如你自主选择使用充值服务，则视为你已充分理解并同意本须知，本须知将作为你与第三方商家就充值服务达成的协议，供双方遵守。","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.ss.android.ugc.aweme","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":true,"boundsInParent":"(26, 330 - 367, 507)","boundsInScreen":"(71, 1132 - 1009, 1619)"},{"index":6,"text":"\n如果你未满18周岁，应在监护人监护、指导下阅读本须知和使用本服务。","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.ss.android.ugc.aweme","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":true,"boundsInParent":"(26, 515 - 367, 591)","boundsInScreen":"(71, 1641 - 1009, 1850)"},{"index":7,"text":"\n一、由平台内第三方商家为你提供充值服务，第三方商家应向你就充值服务提供发票。\n第三方商家提供的充值服务策略及具体内容由第三方商家决定，具体服务情况请咨询该第三方商家。","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.ss.android.ugc.aweme","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":true,"boundsInParent":"(26, 600 - 367, 751)","boundsInScreen":"(71, 1875 - 1009, 2290)"},{"index":8,"text":"\n二、你同意，你应当确保在线提交充值的手机号码、其他充值号码（如QQ号、微信号充值）填写正确、无误，如因你充值号码填写错误等个人原因造成任何损失的，平台、第三方商家就此不向你承担任何责任。","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.ss.android.ugc.aweme","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":true,"boundsInParent":"(26, 760 - 367, 911)","boundsInScreen":"(71, 2315 - 1009, 2401)"},{"index":9,"text":"\n三、 充值失败时，充值款项将根据账户类型及支付渠道进行原路退回。","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.ss.android.ugc.aweme","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":false,"boundsInParent":"(26, 920 - 367, 996)","boundsInScreen":"(71, 2755 - 1009, 2401)"},{"index":10,"text":"\n四、你可以通过抖音App\/抖音极速版的【我】- 【抖音商城】-【我的订单】，或者抖音火山版App的【好物】-右上角【订单】查看和管理你的订单信息。","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.ss.android.ugc.aweme","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":false,"boundsInParent":"(26, 1004 - 367, 1131)","boundsInScreen":"(71, 2986 - 1009, 2401)"},{"index":11,"text":"\n五、请根据你所需充值服务类型，阅读第三方商家具体服务须知。","class":"android.view.View","package":"com.ss.android.ugc.aweme","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"isVisibleToUser":false,"boundsInParent":"(26, 1139 - 367, 1216)","boundsInScreen":"(71, 3357 - 1009, 2401)"}]}]}]}]}